Class DummyDataHelper

java.lang.Object
com.example.theaterproject.Helpers.DummyDataHelper
public class DummyDataHelper extends Object
Helper class for generating dummy data for testing and development purposes. Provides methods to create sample instances of various model classes such as Movies, Accounts, Screenings, Showrooms, and Tickets.
